data.description: SOLAR PANELS TO BE PAID OFF AT CLOSING! Welcome to the quiet community of Wintergreen Ridge minutes from I-20 and I-35. It boasts close proximity to Amusements Parks, parks, walking trails and shopping. This beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom has too many features to list. The extended foyer offers a study (that can be used as a formal dining, formal living area, den or flex space) that is perfect for everyday use. Tuck away in the corner is your Primary bedroom that offers enough space for sitting area or personal workout space, with a primary ensuite to envy. Your inviting kitchen is a chefs dream allowing you to still be apart of the entertainment as you prepare Sunday Best. Upstairs offers secondary bedrooms with separate vanities, Jack N Jill bathroom along with walk in closets. Your game room allows multi use as a media room, bonus room, 4th bedroom or a second primary bedroom on the second floor. With all this space and possibilities your imagination is the limit. WELCOME HOME!
